Task Statement 2.1: Implement scalability and elasticity.
Create and maintain AWS Auto Scaling plans.

Elastic Load Balancing works with Amazon EC2 Auto Scaling to:
 distribute incoming traffic across your healthy Amazon EC2 instances. 
 This increases the scalability and availability of your application. 
 You can enable Elastic Load Balancing within multiple Availability Zones to increase the fault tolerance of your applications.

 Implement caching.
 Implement Amazon RDS replicas and Amazon Aurora Replicas.
 Implement loosely coupled architectures.
 Differentiate between horizontal scaling and vertical scaling.
